net.openhft.chronicle.queue.reader

Interface ChronicleReaderPlugin


  • public interface ChronicleReaderPlugin
    Handle the document from the queue that is read in ChronicleReader. Particularly useful when you need more than the text representation e.g. when your queue is written in binary.
